            State's consent. He needs to go a bit further and&#x2014;this is the point of the amendment tabled by the noble Lord, Lord Bradshaw&#x2014;restore the position, so that local people are able to specify their local services. They are democratically accountable and are the people who should be able to say, "This is the sort of rail service that we want in our area".
