      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0670P0-01953'>
        <a name='S5LV0670P0_20050303_GCR_118'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-herbert-cayzer-2' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0670P0_20050303_GCR_118' title='Link to this speech by Mr Herbert Cayzer' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-herbert-cayzer-2" title="Mr Herbert Cayzer">Lord Rotherwick</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.</p><p>
            Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.</p><p>
            <span class="italic">[Amendments Nos. 63 and 64 not moved.]</span></p><p>
            Clause 33 agreed to.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0670P0-01954'>
        <a name='S5LV0670P0_20050303_GCR_119'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-christine-crawley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
