          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-christine-crawley" title="Ms Christine Crawley">Baroness Crawley</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This may be a convenient moment to adjourn the Committee until Wednesday next at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0670P0-01955'>
